            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Deactivate the alternate screen.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">alternate_screen_off</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9118401753-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9118401753-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9118401753-2">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[?1049l\e[23;0;0t&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="9118401753-2">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
