            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Change foreground (aka text) color to index color. <code class="inline">Index</code> 0-15 are equivalent to
the named colors in <a href="#t:foreground_color/0"><code class="inline">foreground_color/0</code></a> in the order that they are listed.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">color</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-1">(</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-2">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[35m&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-2">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">color</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-3">(</span><span class="mi">80</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-4">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[38;5;80m&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5817036337-4">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
