<section class="detail" id="cursor_get_position/0">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#cursor_get_position/0" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">




              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">cursor_get_position()<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">Result</span></h1>




          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L1848" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Result = {Row :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:non_neg_integer/0">non_neg_integer</a>(), Column :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:non_neg_integer/0">non_neg_integer</a>()} | {error, <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>()}</pre>

        </div>


<p>Get the current cursor position as {Row, Column}.
Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup bash" translate="no"><span class="">## Enter noshell-raw mode and request cursor location and then print
</span><span class="">## the reply to stdout.
</span><span class="gp unselectable">$ </span><span class="">erl -noshell -eval &#39;shell:start_interactive({noshell,raw}),
</span><span class="">    {Row,Col} = io_ansi:cursor_get_position(),
</span><span class="">    io:format(&quot;~p&quot;,[{Row,Col}])&#39; -s init stop
</span><span class="">{58,1}
</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
