<section class="detail" id="cursor_horizontal_vertical/2">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#cursor_horizontal_vertical/2" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">


            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">cursor_horizontal_vertical(X :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>(), Y :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>())<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="unicode.html#t:chardata/0">unicode:chardata</a>()</span></h1>



          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L1809" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">X = Y = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Move the cursor to line <code class="inline">X</code> and column <code class="inline">Y</code>. Position 1,1 is at the top left of the
terminal.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_horizontal_vertical</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3335953167-1">(</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3335953167-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3335953167-2">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[10;20f&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3335953167-2">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="cursor_move/2">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#cursor_move/2" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">




              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">cursor_move(DeltaLine, DeltaColumn)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="unicode.html#t:chardata/0">unicode:chardata</a>()</span></h1>




          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L1571" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">DeltaLine = DeltaColumn = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Move the cursor relative to its current position.</p><p>Positive <code class="inline">DeltaLine</code> moves down, negative moves up.
Positive <code class="inline">DeltaColumn</code> moves right (forward), negative moves left (backward).</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_move</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-1">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-2">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[5A&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-2">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_move</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-3">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-4">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[10C&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-4">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_move</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-5">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-6">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[3B\e[2D&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-6">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">4&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_move</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-7">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-7">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-8">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="6356027599-8">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
