<section class="detail" id="cursor_report_position/0">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#cursor_report_position/0" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">


            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">cursor_report_position()<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="unicode.html#t:chardata/0">unicode:chardata</a>()</span></h1>



          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L1832" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Instruct the terminal to report the current cursor position.</p><p>Examples:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">cursor_report_position</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4207694183-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4207694183-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="s">~&quot;</span><span class="se">\e</span><span class="s">[6n&quot;</span></code></pre><pre><code class="makeup bash" translate="no"><span class="">## Enter noshell-raw mode and request cursor location and then print
</span><span class="">## the reply to stdout.
</span><span class="gp unselectable">$ </span><span class="">erl -noshell -eval &#39;shell:start_interactive({noshell,raw}),
</span><span class="">    io_ansi:fwrite([cursor_report_position]),
</span><span class="">    io:format(&quot;~p&quot;,[io:get_chars(&quot;&quot;,20)])&#39; -s init stop
</span><span class="">&quot;\e[58;1R&quot;
</span></code></pre><p>The reported cursor position in the example is row 58 and column 1 both are 1 index based.</p>
  </section>
</section>
