<p>Check if <a href="io.html#t:user/0"><code class="inline">io:user/0</code></a> can interpret ANSI escape sequences.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">enabled</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2615959075-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2615959075-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">true</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="enabled/1">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#enabled/1" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">


            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">enabled(Device :: <a href="io.html#t:device/0">io:device</a>())<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:boolean/0">boolean</a>()</span></h1>



          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L2149" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Check if <code class="inline">Device</code> can interpret ANSI escape sequences.</p><p>This is done by checking if <code class="inline">Device</code> represents a terminal and if the <code class="inline">TERM</code>
environment variable is set to a terminal type that supports virtual terminal
sequences.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">enabled</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-1">(</span><span class="ss">standard_error</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">true</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-2">{</span><span class="ss">ok</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">File</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-2">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">file</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">open</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-3">(</span><span class="s">&quot;tmp&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-4">[</span><span class="ss">write</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-4">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-3">)</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">enabled</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-5">(</span><span class="n">File</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3063378500-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">false</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="erase_character/1">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#erase_character/1" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
    <div class="heading-with-actions">

      <div class="signature-row">


            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">erase_character(Chars :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>())<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="unicode.html#t:chardata/0">unicode:chardata</a>()</span></h1>



          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20028@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/io_ansi.erl#L1450" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
            <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Erase <code class="inline">Chars</code> characters at cursor by making <code class="inline">Chars</code> characters before the cursor blank.</p><p>Example:</p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">io_ansi</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">erase_character</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3249196495-1">(</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3249196495-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3249196495-2">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;\e[4X&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3249196495-2">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
